title: Should this run League at 60 FPS?
body:
Acer Aspire E5-575-57A4
-I5 (7th gen) 7500 CPU 2.5 GHZ (3.1) Turbo
-Nvidia GeForce 950M 2GB 
-8 GB DDR4 Ram
-1 TB HDD, 256GB SSD

FPS won't go passed 30 FPS, turned down all settings and still stuck at 30 FPS.  FPS uncapped.

My old system had 16 GB ram, I7 2700k and a measly GTX 750 and ran at constant 60 FPS.  I've seen this laptop exceed 100 FPS on youtube with a 6200u processor and a 940m.  Any ideas?
